channel.title: Problem with uploading new cache after adding to dropbox =(
channel.description:
Hi i am having a problem with my cache in my server!! i uploaded to dropbox and i changed all the files in my source and client with my dropbox new cache and deleted old cache from my c drive and when i go to run my server it gives me a huge error it dont download my new cache for my server . I checked the specified path all the way to mapConfiguration and it still says it cant find it. Please look in to the picture i posted to see if anyone know the answer to this problem i will be very greatfull i really need to fix this. I tried just about everything i could. Thanks to all that take a lil time to help me out.
[img]http://www.upload.ee/image/4272258/error.jpg[/img]

item.title: Problem with uploading new cache after adding to dropbox =(
item.dc:creator: @lol_space1 lol space
item.description:
@lol_space1 wrote:

It’s saying that your mapConfig file is missing in the cache directory…


just goto your cache folder/maps/ and add mapConfig.java in or there may be another file already in there with a similar name, just change it .
